meta.description: Canonical Place (Incorporated Cities/Towns/Villages) GEOIDs by State
meta.format: GEOID FORMAT: SSPPPPP (State FIPS 2 digits + Place FIPS 5 digits)
specialCases: New England states (ME, MA, NH, RI, VT) use Minor Civil Divisions (MCDs) as primary local government, so their incorporated place counts are lower
Virginia: Includes independent cities (e.g., Richmond, Norfolk)
Consolidated city-counties (San Francisco, Denver) have single GEOID
